'''Bahn''' was one of the three neighborhoods in [[Tof Soren]] on [[Ord Vaxal]]. Bahn peacekeepers carried heavy clubs and cudgels. They could be identified by purple diamond-shaped [[Tattoo/Legends|tattoos]] below their [[Eye/Legends|eyes]].

